SET timezone = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

WITH 
    my_listings AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT
            l.id as listing_id
            , m.name AS model
            , br.name AS brand
            , l.registration_no
            , INITCAP(CONCAT(h.first_name, ' ', h.last_name)) AS host_name
            , INITCAP(h.first_name) AS host_first_name
            , h.email AS host_email
            , concat(ll.address_line_1,' ',ll.address_line_2,' ',ll.state_region_province,' ',ll.postal_code) AS listing_address
            , cc.percent
            , l.url as listing_url
            , l.is_instant
        FROM listings l
            JOIN listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
            JOIN listing_commission_class lcc ON lcc.listing_id = l.id
            JOIN commission_class cc ON cc.id = lcc.commission_id
            JOIN users h ON h.id = l.user_id
            JOIN models m ON m.id = l.model_id
            JOIN brands br ON br.id = m.brand_id
        WHERE 1=1
            AND ll.country = 'Malaysia'
            --and h.id IN (5162, 34411, 11182)
    )   
    
    , my_bookings AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT
            b.id as booking_id
            , b.ref_no AS id
            , TO_CHAR(b.created_at, 'dd Mon yyyy, hh12:miAM') AS created_at
            , b.created_at AS booking_created
            , CASE
                WHEN l.is_instant = true THEN b.created_at
                ELSE ht.created_at END AS accepted_at
            , TO_CHAR(b.request_start_at, 'Dy, dd Mon') AS request_start_date
            , TO_CHAR(b.request_start_at, 'hh12:miAM') AS request_start_time
            , TO_CHAR(b.request_end_at, 'Dy, dd Mon') AS request_end_date
            , TO_CHAR(b.request_end_at, 'hh12:miAM') AS request_end_time
            --, to_char(b.request_end_at::timestamp, 'YYYY-MM') AS request_end_month
            , date_trunc('month', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date AS request_end_month
            , CASE
                WHEN bl.pricing_id = '3' THEN 0.5
                WHEN ( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400 < 1 THEN 1
                WHEN ( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at)::INT - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at) :: INT )%86400 < 2160 THEN FLOOR((EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400)
                ELSE CEIL(( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400)
                END AS days_booked
            , TO_CHAR(( CASE
                WHEN bl.pricing_id = '3' THEN 0.5
                WHEN ( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at)- EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400 < 1 THEN 1
                WHEN ( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) :: INT - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at) :: INT )%86400 < 2160 THEN FLOOR((EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400)
                ELSE CEIL(( EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_end_at) - EXTRACT(epoch FROM b.request_start_at)) / 86400)
                END ) * 200, '9999') AS mileage
            , b.gross_amount as gmv
            , bl.amount as rental
            , to_char(bl.amount * (1-l.percent/100), '9999.99') as commission
            , to_char(bl.amount - (bl.amount * (1-l.percent/100)), '9999.99') as marketplace_fee
            , to_char(bl.amount * ( l.PERCENT / 100 ) * 0.08, '9999.99') AS service_tax
            , TO_CHAR(bl.amount - bl.amount * ( l.percent / 100 ) - bl.amount * ( l.percent / 100 ) * 0.08, '9999.99') AS payout_after_service_tax
            , CASE
                WHEN MOD(to_char(b.request_end_at :: timestamp, 'IW')::integer,2) != 0 THEN to_char(date_trunc('week', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date + interval'14 days', 'dd Mon yyyy')
                ELSE to_char(date_trunc('week', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date + interval'7 days', 'dd Mon yyyy')
                END AS payout_week_start
            , CASE
                WHEN mod(to_char(b.request_end_at :: timestamp, 'IW')::integer,2) != 0 THEN to_char(date_trunc('week', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date + interval'20 days','dd Mon yyyy')
                ELSE to_char(date_trunc('week', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date + interval'13 days','dd Mon yyyy')
                END AS payout_week_end
            -- Guest Details
            , INITCAP(CONCAT(u.first_name, ' ', u.last_name)) AS guest_display_name
            , INITCAP(u.first_name) AS guest_first_name
            , INITCAP(u.last_name) AS guest_last_name
            , u.email as guest_email
            , concat(u.phone_country_code, u.phone_number) AS guest_phone
            --Listing Details
            , b.listing_id
            , model
            , brand
            , registration_no
            , host_name
            , host_first_name
            , host_email
            , listing_address
            , listing_url
            -- Mileage Details
            , TO_CHAR(mf.amount/0.6, '9999') AS mileage_purchased
        FROM bookings b
            LEFT JOIN booking_lines bl ON bl.booking_id = b.id
                AND bl.slug = 'rental-fee'
            LEFT JOIN booking_lines mf ON mf.booking_id = b.id
                AND mf.slug = 'mileage-fee'
            LEFT JOIN host_tracking ht ON ht.booking_id = b.id
            JOIN users u ON u.id = b.user_id
            JOIN my_listings l on l.listing_id = b.listing_id
        WHERE 1=1
            AND b.status in ('requested')
        ORDER BY 2 DESC
    )
    
    , guest_delivery_addresses AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT
            bd.booking_id
            , MAX(concat(uad.address_line_1,' ',uad.address_line_2,' ',uad.state_region_province,' ',uad.postal_code)) as delivery_address
            , MAX(concat(uac.address_line_1,' ',uac.address_line_2,' ',uac.state_region_province,' ',uac.postal_code)) as collection_address
        FROM booking_deliveries bd
        LEFT JOIN user_address uad ON uad.id = bd.delivery_id AND bd.type = 'car-drop-off'
        LEFT JOIN user_address uac ON uac.id = bd.delivery_id AND bd.type = 'car-pick-up'
        WHERE 1=1
        GROUP BY 1
    )

    , est_earnings AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT 
          b.listing_id
          --, to_char(b.request_end_at::timestamp, 'YYYY-MM')AS month
          , date_trunc('month', b.request_end_at :: timestamp) :: date AS request_end_month
          , sum(d5.rental - (d5.rental*(cc.PERCENT/100)))  AS est_earnings
        FROM bookings b
        LEFT JOIN listings l ON l.id = b.listing_id
        LEFT JOIN listing_commission_class lcc ON lcc.listing_id = b.listing_id
        LEFT JOIN commission_class cc ON cc.id = lcc.commission_id
        LEFT JOIN (
           SELECT bl.booking_id, bl.amount AS rental
           FROM booking_lines bl
           WHERE  bl.slug = 'rental-fee'
         ) d5 ON b.id = d5.booking_id
        WHERE b.status IN ('accepted','waiting_for_inspection','start_driving','return_car','completed')
        GROUP BY 1,2
    )
    
SELECT
    -- Booking Details
    b.id as ref_no
    , created_at as created_time
    , accepted_at
    , request_start_date as start_date
    , request_start_time as start_time
    , request_end_date as end_date
    , request_end_time as end_time
    , days_booked as duration
    , mileage as free_mileage
    -- Payout Details
    , gmv 
    , rental as rental_rate
    , commission as gross_payout
    , marketplace_fee
    , service_tax as sst
    , payout_after_service_tax as net_payout
    , payout_week_start as payout_start
    , payout_week_end as payout_end
    , est_earnings as total_estimated_po
    -- Guest Details
    , guest_display_name
    , guest_first_name
    , guest_last_name
    , guest_email 
    , guest_phone
    --Listing Details
    , model
    , brand
    , registration_no as car_plate
    , host_name 
    , host_first_name as host_firstname
    , host_email
    , listing_address 
    , listing_url as url
    -- Delivery Details
    , CASE WHEN delivery_address IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE delivery_address END AS delivery_address
    , CASE WHEN collection_address IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE collection_address END AS collection_address
    -- Additional Mileage Details
    , CASE WHEN mileage_purchased IS NULL THEN 'N/A' ELSE mileage_purchased END AS mileage_purchased
FROM my_bookings b
LEFT JOIN guest_delivery_addresses d on d.booking_id = b.booking_id
LEFT JOIN est_earnings e on e.request_end_month = b.request_end_month 
    AND e.listing_id = b.listing_id 
WHERE 1=1
    AND b.booking_created >= now() - interval '1 hours'
